<a id="date" style="display:none">2012-08-12</a><h1 style="clear: both;">Veep calls for nation to celebrate life of President Mills</h1>
<div class="option-bar">
<p><a rel="nofollow" href="artikel.php?ID=247413&nav=previous">&laquo; Prev</a></p><p><a rel="nofollow" href="artikel.php?ID=247413&nav=next">Next &raquo;</a></p><p class="last"><a href="artikel.php?ID=247413&comment=0#com" rel="nofollow">Comments (0)</a></p>
